:\".opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts/tests/skill-benchmark.vitest.ts\",\"line\":190,\"issue\":\"E2E test creates temp dir (mkdtempSync lc-e2e-) but never cleans it up — resource leak in test hygiene\",\"fix\":\"Add afterAll cleanup: try { rmSync(out, { recursive: true }) } catch {}\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i7-05\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"file\":\".opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/router-replay.cjs\",\"line\":22,\"issue\":\"AMBIGUITY_DELTA=1 boundary (score diff exactly 1, delta=0, empty scores) is not exercised by any test — selectIntents edge cases are uncovered\",\"fix\":\"Add test cases for equal scores (delta=0), score gap >1 (only top kept), and zero intents\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-hs-i7-06\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"file\":\".opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts/tests/skill-benchmark.vitest.ts\",\"line\":124,\"issue\":\"Negative-activation scoring (expected.negativeActivation=true) is only tested with a hand-constructed routerResult; no fixture pair or integration test exercises a real negative-activation scenario end-to-end\",\"fix\":\"Author a negative-activation fixture pair or add run-skill-benchmark-level test verifying dims.d3.score===0 for negative scenarios\"}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-007.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-007.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/006-deep-review/review/hs/deltas/iter-007.jsonl","time":{"start":1780205178841,"end":1780205178861}},"id":"prt_e7c7f21de001v